        <description>&lt;p&gt;One of the standout features of &lt;em&gt;Directory Opus&lt;/em&gt; is its capability to manage multiple listers and a multitude of open tabs. However, this flexibility can quickly lead to a cluttered workspace if redundant tabs aren&amp;rsquo;t regularly closed.&lt;/p&gt;
