        <description>&lt;p&gt;One of the best features of &lt;em&gt;Directory Opus&lt;/em&gt; is the ability to have multiple listers with numerous open tabs. However, if you&amp;rsquo;re not diligent in closing unnecessary tabs, you&amp;rsquo;ll quickly end up with a cluttered mix of relevant and irrelevant tabs.&lt;/p&gt;
